# 📖 Chapter 06 – Off-Page SEO

---

# 🎯 Chapter Objective

Is chapter me hum Off-Page SEO ko detail me samjhenge. Aap seekhenge ki website ke bahar ki jane wali SEO activities kya hoti hain, backlinks kaise kaam karte hain, Domain Authority kya hoti hai, link building kaise ki jati hai aur Google website ki authority kaise evaluate karta hai.

---

# 6.1 What is Off-Page SEO?

**Off-Page SEO** website ke bahar ki jane wali optimization process hai jiska objective website ki authority, trust aur reputation ko improve karna hota hai.

Simple Words:

> **Off-Page SEO = Website ke bahar ki jane wali activities jo Google ko batati hain ki aapki website trustworthy aur valuable hai.**

Agar On-Page SEO website ka content improve karta hai, to Off-Page SEO website ki reputation build karta hai.

---

# 6.2 Why is Off-Page SEO Important?

Google sirf content nahi dekhta.

Wo ye bhi dekhta hai ki:

* Kitni websites aapko recommend kar rahi hain.
* Aapki brand kitni trusted hai.
* Log aapki website ke baare me kya bol rahe hain.

Benefits:

* Better Google Rankings
* Higher Domain Authority
* More Referral Traffic
* Better Brand Trust
* Faster Indexing
* Long-Term SEO Growth

---

# 6.3 On-Page SEO vs Off-Page SEO

| On-Page SEO                   | Off-Page SEO                  |
| ----------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Website ke andar optimization | Website ke bahar optimization |
| Content Improve karta hai     | Authority Improve karta hai   |
| Keywords Optimize karta hai   | Backlinks Build karta hai     |
| Technical Changes             | Reputation Building           |

Dono equally important hain.

---

# 6.4 What is a Backlink?

**Backlink** ek link hota hai jo kisi dusri website se aapki website ki taraf aata hai.

Example:

```text id="o5f0jx"
Industry Blog

↓

Links to

↓

SafePro Fire Services
```

Google ise ek recommendation ke roop me dekhta hai.

Jitne quality backlinks honge, utni authority improve hogi.

---

# 6.5 Types of Backlinks

## 1. DoFollow Backlinks

Google authority pass karta hai.

SEO ke liye sabse valuable.

---

## 2. NoFollow Backlinks

Authority pass nahi karte.

Lekin traffic aur brand visibility ke liye useful hote hain.

---

# 6.6 High Quality vs Low Quality Backlinks

### High Quality

* Relevant Website
* Trusted Website
* High Authority
* Natural Link

Examples:

* Government Websites
* Educational Websites
* Industry Blogs
* News Websites

---

### Low Quality

* Spam Websites
* Irrelevant Directories
* Link Farms
* Paid Spam Links

Google spammy backlinks ko ignore ya penalize kar sakta hai.

---

# 6.7 Domain Authority (DA)

**Domain Authority (DA)** ek score hai jo estimate karta hai ki website search results me kitni strong compete kar sakti hai.

Range:

```text id="2eqv8r"
1 → New Website

100 → Extremely Strong Website
```

Higher DA generally better authority ko indicate karta hai.

> Note: DA Google ka official metric nahi hai, lekin SEO industry me widely use hota hai.

---

# 6.8 Page Authority (PA)

Page Authority kisi specific webpage ki strength ko indicate karta hai.

Example:

Homepage ki PA aur Blog Page ki PA alag ho sakti hai.

---

# 6.9 Link Building

**Link Building** ka matlab quality backlinks earn karna hai.

Common Methods:

