# 6.11 Social Signals

Google directly social media likes ko ranking factor nahi maanta, lekin social media se:

* Brand Awareness
* Website Traffic
* Content Reach
* Natural Backlinks

mil sakte hain.

Platforms:

* LinkedIn
* Facebook
* Instagram
* X (Twitter)
* YouTube

---

# 6.12 Brand Mentions

Agar koi website aapki company ka naam mention karti hai, chahe link na bhi de, to usse brand authority improve ho sakti hai.

Example:

> "SafePro Fire Services is one of the leading fire safety companies in Mumbai."

---

# 6.13 Guest Posting

Guest Posting me aap kisi dusri website ke liye article likhte hain aur us article me apni website ka backlink include karte hain.

Benefits:

* High Quality Backlinks
* Brand Exposure
* Referral Traffic
* Authority Build Hoti Hai

---

# 6.14 Broken Link Building

Kisi website par broken link identify karo.

Uske owner ko inform karo.

Apna relevant page suggest karo.

Agar wo replace karta hai to quality backlink mil sakta hai.

